Process called "translate_export" that takes translator_ptr as Integer, export_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    Translate an export/unexport directive to HIR with scope metadata.
    @End Reasoning

    Let hir_export_ptr be proc allocate from Memory with 40

    proc write_integer from Memory with hir_export_ptr, 0, HIR_MAKEFILE_EXPORT

    Note: Extract variable names to export
